         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">New Year's Day 1888. ¶  ¶ The happy duty still remains for me, dear Mr Tepper, to express my best thanks to you for the kind wishes that you again offer me at this festive season and have accompanied ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">88.01.01a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Otto Tepper</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">RB MSS M198, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">Neujahrstag 1888.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Es bleibt mir noch die freudige Pflicht, lieber Herr Tepper, Ihnen meinen besten Dank auszusprechen für die gütigen Wünsche, welche Sie mir zu dieser Festzeit wieder darbringen, u mit einem so schönen Souvenir begleitet haben.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Möge denn auch die neue annuella Spanne Zeit, in welche wir jetzt hineinleben, reich an Freuden für </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Sie</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> sein, und Ihnen neuen Ruhm in Ihren erfolgreichen Streben für die Wissenschaften bringen!</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">New Year's Day 1888.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The happy duty still remains for me, dear Mr Tepper, to express my best thanks to you for the kind wishes that you again offer me at this festive season and have accompanied with such a beautiful souvenir.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>May the new annual span of time, in which we now live, also be rich in joy for <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">you</hi>
               </seg> and bring you new glory in your successful efforts for the sciences!<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">See also M to O. Tepper, 20 December 1887 (in this edition as 87-12-20b).</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
         </div>
      </body>
